+/**
+ * Parse the VS_FIXEDFILEINFO version from a Windows PE binary.
+ * Works on any platform — reads the raw .rsrc section bytes.
+ * Returns '0.0.0' on any parse failure; never throws.
+ *
+ * @param {string} filePath  Path to a Windows PE executable
+ * @param {boolean} useProduct  true = read dwProductVersion, false = read dwFileVersion
+ * @returns {string}  Version string "major.minor.patch.build" or '0.0.0'
